ActTerritorial Lands Act
PrecisORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN NUNAVUT (NORTHERN BATHURST ISLAND NATIONAL PARK, NUNAVUT) - which provides for (a) the withdrawal from disposal of some 11,800 square kilometres of land in order to facilitate the establishment of a proposed national park; and (b) the repeal of a similar Withdrawal from Disposal Order made in 2001.
